            desc: "If your task got declined, check the reason behind the decline. Fix the issues mentioned in the reason and re-submit your task.",
            icon: "question"}) %>

            <%- include("partials/help_info_article.ejs", {
            title: "Can i re-submit if my task got approved but I got low marks for it?",
            desc: "No, you cannot re-submit if your task already got approved",
            icon: "question"}) %>

            <%- include("partials/help_info_article.ejs", {
            title: "Where can I know whether my task/quiz got approved",
            desc: "When a task/quiz gets approved/evaluated an email is sent out to the email you specified when you registered. If you do not see it in your inbox, make sure it isn't in the spam folder. If it isn't in the spam folder either, reach out to our team.",
            icon: "question"}) %>

            <%- include("partials/help_info_article.ejs", {
            title: "What are advanced tasks?",
            desc: "Advanced tasks are a type of task that gets released near the end of the competition. Advanced are more challenging and offer more points compared to normal tasks.",
            icon: "question"}) %>

            <%- include("partials/help_info_article.ejs", {
            title: "How many points do I get per task/quiz?",
            desc: "Normal tasks are scored out of 10, while advanced tasks are scored out of 100. And quizzes are scored out of 20 with the top three places receiving extra points",
            icon: "question"}) %>
